		<title>Humour in the Bible 10: 2 Samuel: God explains ‘himself’</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/5minutebible/tlRR/~3/oCwTenZqCTQ/</link>
		<comments>http://5minutebible.com/humour-in-the-bible-10-2-samuel-god-explains-himself/#comments</comments>
