		<feedburner:origLink>http://5minutebible.com/humour-in-the-bible-10-2-samuel-god-explains-himself/</feedburner:origLink></item>
		<item>
		<title>Humour in the Bible 9: 1 Samuel: Introducing Saul</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/5minutebible/tlRR/~3/8_CW_yoz58k/</link>
