		<title>Jonah 1:4-5 : Big!</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/5minutebible/tlRR/~3/xtbk2aXj_4Y/</link>
		<comments>http://5minutebible.com/jonah-14-5-big/#comments</comments>
