			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Jeremiah gets more personal in his complaints, but his &#8220;conversation&#8221; with YHWH still seems to shut out any response&#8230; curiouser and curiouser&#8230; and which ending will you choose of this series?</p>
<p style="text-align: right;">.</p>
